'''批判社區心理學''' (英文：Critical Community Psychology)是一個新的領域，主要為「批判心理學」([[:en:critical_psychology|Critical Psychology]])與「[[社區心理學|社區心理學]]」([[:en:community_psychology|Community Psychology]])的結合體。換言之，從而開啟[[社區心理學|社區心理學]]家獻身於基進([[:en:Radical_Psychology_Network|radical]])與解放([[:en:Liberation_psychology|liberation]])相關實際行動。<ref name="ref1">{{cite book |last= Lewis |first= Judith A. |coauthors= Michael D. Lewis, Judy A. Daniels, Michael J. D’Andrea|title= '' Community Counseling: Empowerment Strategies for a Diverse Society '' |publisher= Brooks/Cole-Thomson Learning] |year= 2003 |isbn= 0-534-50626-7 }}</ref><ref name="ref2">{{cite conference |first=Carolyn |last= Kagan |coauthors = Mark Burton |date=2001-March |title= Critical Community Psychology Praxis for the 21st Century |conference = British Psychological Society Conference |location= Glasgow |accessdate= 2009-12-30}}</ref>



== 批判社區心理學的發展背景== 

*目前許多人們的生活狀況直接受到[[全球化|全球化]]、[[失業|失業]]與[[歧視|歧視]]等影響。<ref name="ref3">{{cite book |last= Orford |first= Jim |title= '' Community Psychology: Challenges, Controversies and Emerging Consensus '' |publisher= John Wiley & Sons, Ltd |year= 2008 |isbn= 978-0-470-85593-5 }}</ref>

*從[[社區心理學|社區心理學]]相關文獻回顧來看，目前已非常少關注在社會行動([[:en:Social_actions|social action]])、倡導(advocacy)、社會改變運動([[:en:social_change|social change]] movements)、貧窮與反貧窮組織(anti-poverty organizations)、[[草根|草根]]社區組織([[:en:community_organizing|community organizing]])、人權([[:en:human_rights|human rights]])、永續社區([[:en:sustainable_community|sustainable community]])經濟發展與社會政策([[:en:social_policy|social policy]])等，尤其是政治面向與相關動力方面。<ref name="ref2" />

